    "Personalization and User Experience.",
    "Contextawareness enables IoT applications to tailor their services and interactions based on individual user preferences, behavior, and situational context.",
    "This personalization enhances user experience by providing relevant and timely information, recommendations, and automation [21].",
    "Real-Time Decision Making.",
    "By considering realtime contextual information, IoT devices and applications can make informed and adaptive decisions."
